Package arithmea.shared.qabalah

Class Summary
SephirothData Class representing the positions of the sephiroth.
 

Enum Summary
HebrewPath Enum to represent the classical 22 paths on the tree of life.
LatinPath Enum to represent the 26 paths on the tree of life associated with the 26 letters in the latin alphabet.
Sephira Enum to represent the ten sephiroth and da'ath.
SephirothData.SephiraPosition Enum calculating the relative sephiroth positions.
